Reason.answer_quality: The page effectively answers this need by providing a clear list of the eligibility criteria.

Reason.next_actions: I would visit the local council's website or call their office to submit my application once I confirm I meet these eligibility criteria.

Reason.need: How quickly I will find out if I'm eligible

Reason.next_actions: I would contact the local council to inquire about the approximate time for processing applications and eligibility determination.
